10 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
11 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 26 O.S. 2021, Section 2-101.9, is
12 amended to read as follows:
13 Section 2-101.9. Members of the State Election Board shall be
14 paid Fifty Dollars ($50.00) Seventy-five Dollars ($75.00) per diem
15 for each meeting for the purpose of conducting hearings required by
16 law, and Thirty-five Dollars ($35.00) Seventy-five Dollars ($75.00)
17 per diem for other meetings, and shall be allowed mileage
18 reimbursement at the rate provided by the State Travel Reimbursement
19 Act, Section 500.1 et seq. of Title 74 of the Oklahoma Statutes.
20 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 26 O.S. 2021, Section 2-115, is
21 amended to read as follows:
22 Section 2-115. The chair and vice-chair of each county election
23 board shall be paid Thirty-five Dollars ($35.00) Seventy-five
24 Dollars ($75.00) per diem in lieu of subsistence for each meeting of
