1 the county election board and shall be allowed mileage reimbursement
2 at the rate prescribed for travel by state employees. The per diem
3 and mileage reimbursement shall be paid by the State Election Board,
4 except for meetings chargeable to other governmental units as
5 provided by law; provided, the State Election Board shall not pay
6 such reimbursement for more than forty meetings per fiscal year.
7 SECTION 3. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
